{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"Integrate-OUDS","text":"Integrate OUDS","type":"heading","level":2},{"anchor":"Use-Swift-Package-Manager","text":"Use Swift Package Manager","type":"heading","level":3},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If you want to add the iOS library of "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Orange Unified Design System"}]},{"type":"text","text":", you need to add our "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Swift Package"}]},{"type":"text","text":" into your project."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"To do that, add a new "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"package dependency"}]},{"type":"text","text":" to your "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Xcode"}]},{"type":"text","text":" project by refering to it by "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"github.com\/Orange-OpenSource\/ouds-ios"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"You are free to choose wether or not you want a branch or a specific tag, pick the solution you want."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You can "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/Orange-OpenSource\/ouds-ios\/wiki\/50-%E2%80%90-About-versions,-releases-and-builds","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" for more details about versions, releases and tags. You can find release tags (e.g. "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"1.0.0","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":") and release candidates tags (e.g. "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"1.0.0-rc3","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":")."}]},{"anchor":"Import-the-librairies-you-need","text":"Import the librairies you need","type":"heading","level":3},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You should use one (or several) of the following imports for your needs, which are basically "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"Swift Package","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" products."}]},{"style":"tip","name":"Tip","type":"aside","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"We recommend to embed in your apps only the ones you need to avoid to embed useless assets.","type":"text"}]}]},{"syntax":"swift","code":["import OUDSThemesContract \/\/ If you want to define your theme, use themes or OUDSThemeableView","import OUDSModules \/\/ To use modules","import OUDSComponents \/\/ To use components","import OUDSThemesOrange \/\/ To use the default Orange theme","import OUDSThemesOrangeCompact \/\/ To use the Orange Compact theme","import OUDSThemesSosh \/\/ To use the Sosh theme","import OUDSThemesWireframe \/\/ To use the Wireframe theme","import OUDSTokensComponent \/\/ If you need to override or use directly components tokens","import OUDSTokenSemantic \/\/ If you need to override or use directly semantic tokens","import OUDSTokensRaw \/\/ If you need to override or use directly raw tokens","import OUDSFoundations \/\/ For some utilities"],"type":"codeListing"},{"anchor":"Or-more-simple-import-umbrella-library","text":"Or more simple, import umbrella library","type":"heading","level":3},{"style":"note","name":"Note","type":"aside","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"We do not recommend this solution because from our point of view use of tailored imports is better to import only the needed elements.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"use of umbrella products can increase app sizes and needed storage because it emebds plenty of assets (images, fonts, etc.)","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"and useless constants.","type":"text"}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Import the "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"Swift Package","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" product which suits your needs:"}]},{"header":"row","type":"table","rows":[[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Umbrella","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Description","type":"text"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"OUDSSwiftUI","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"All librairies listed above and all themes","type":"text"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"OUDSSwiftUIOrange","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"All librairies listed above but with only Orange and Orange Compact themes","type":"text"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"OUDSSwiftUIWireframe","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"All librairies listed above but with only Wireframe theme","type":"text"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"OUDSSwiftUIOrangeSosh","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"All librairies listed above but with only Orange and Sosh themes","type":"text"}]}]]]},{"anchor":"Chose-your-theme","text":"Chose your theme","type":"heading","level":3},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"Orange Unified Design System","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" framework provides today four themes:"}]},{"header":"row","type":"table","rows":[[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Theme","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Description","type":"text"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Orange","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The default one for Orange products and can be enriched \/ derivated","type":"text"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Orange Compact","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"For some Orange products with heavy \/ rich UI and dimensions constraints","type":"text"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Sosh","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"For Sosh products","type":"text"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Wireframe","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"For mockups, prototypes and prooves of concepts witouth Orange-flavoured styles","type":"text"}]}]]]},{"anchor":"Apply-a-theme","text":"Apply a theme","type":"heading","level":3},{"columns":[{"size":1,"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You will need to use for your application root view the "},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/ios.unified-design-system.orange.com\/documentation\/ouds\/oudsthemeableview\/","type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/ios.unified-design-system.orange.com\/documentation\/ouds\/themes","type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" also."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This special view is here to define some elements as environment variables and injects the choosen theme."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"size":1,"content":[{"code":["@main","struct YourApp: App {","    var body: some Scene {","       WindowGroup {","          OUDSThemeableView(theme: OrangeTheme()) {","                \/\/ Your root view","          }","       }","    }","}"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"}]}],"type":"row","numberOfColumns":2},{"columns":[{"size":1,"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Then get the current applied theme in your views and use the tokens you want."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The tokens are wrapped in providers with clear names, you only need to choose the ones you want."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"size":1,"content":[{"code":["\/\/ Use it in views as an environment variable","@Environment(\\.theme) var theme"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"}]}],"type":"row","numberOfColumns":2},{"style":"tip","name":"Tip","type":"aside","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Keep in mind only one theme can be used within one ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSThemeableView","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"}]}]},{"anchor":"Trick-for-Xcode-Preview","text":"Trick for Xcode Preview","type":"heading","level":3},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If you use Xcode "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"#Preview"},{"type":"text","text":" blocks, you will have to be sure the theme is instanciated and injected through the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSThemeableView"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Because it is not possible today to override the legit "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"#Preview"},{"type":"text","text":" block, you can instead use some of our utilities to wrap your content"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"inside the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSThemeableView"},{"type":"text","text":" automatically. These utilities come with the themes modules. Without them you may face errors about undefined theme."}]},{"syntax":"swift","code":["\/\/ Apply Orange theme","#Preview {","    SampleView()","        .orangePreview()","}","","\/\/ Apply Orange Compact theme","#Preview {","    SampleView()","        .orangeCompactPreview()","}","","\/\/ Apply Sosh theme","#Preview {","    SampleView()","        .soshPreview()","}","","\/\/ Apply Wireframe theme","#Preview {","    SampleView()","        .wireframePreview()","}"],"type":"codeListing"}]}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/oudsthemescontract\/gettingstarted"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"metadata":{"title":"Getting Started with OUDS","role":"article","images":[{"identifier":"ic_unified_ds.png","type":"icon"},{"identifier":"ic_unified_ds.png","type":"card"}],"modules":[{"name":"Welcome to Orange Unified Design System"}],"roleHeading":"Article"},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OU